title: Dugali Alti
description: Dugali Alti or Dugali Alti di Ostiano is an archaeological site located near Ostiano in Cremona, Italy, that has provided evidence of agricultural practices in the Neolithic period of northern Italy.

properties.description: Point based on an OpenStreetMap node representing Dugali Alti after Biagi 1995.
properties.title: OSM location of Dugali Alti Neolithic Site
